'''Benok's blaster''' was the personal weapon of [[Loppak Slusk]]'s [[Benok|chief of security]]. It had an additional ion cell that allowed it to deal damage to droids. Benok was highly praised on the Citadel Station for his [[Dueling|Master Dueling]] ability.

